import { Heading, Skeleton, Stack } from '@chakra-ui/core';

const Loading = () => (
  <Stack
    width="60%"
    maxWidth="500px"
    minWidth="300px"
    margin="auto"
    spacing="0.5rem"
  >
    <Heading as="h4" size="lg">
      Loading
    </Heading>
    <Skeleton borderRadius="1rem">Placeholder</Skeleton>
    <Skeleton borderRadius="1rem">Placeholder</Skeleton>
    <Skeleton borderRadius="1rem">Placeholder</Skeleton>
    <Skeleton borderRadius="1rem">Placeholder</Skeleton>
  </Stack>
);

export default Loading;
